  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK737">
<l>irupuṉalum vāynta malaiyum varupuṉalum</l>
<l>vallaraṇu nāṭṭiṟ kuṟuppu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The constituents of a kingdom are the two waters (from above and below), well situated hills and an undestructible fort.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
